<ab facs="#facs_337_r1l27">Clas vvollſak <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vormunde des peter <expan>hornu<ex>n</ex>gs</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_337_r1l28"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>ſelıge<ex>n</ex></expan> kinde . vvie Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ kinden noch ettvvieuil </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_337_r1l29">ſchuldig bleibt / darümb ſie ewrn brief mit ſampt <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
