<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Erwirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Schücz und Clas Wollsak,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, vormunde des Peter
                            <expan>Hornu<ex>n</ex>gs</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan> kinde, wie ir
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> kinden noch ettwievil schuldig bleibt,
                        darümb sie ewrn brief mitsampt <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> pürgen
                        insigeln besigelt <expan>ynnehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, dieselb schulde in
                        etwie lang <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan> sey worden, des die kinden
                        schaden nemen. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                    <add><expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> schulde</add> den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>vormunde<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        kinde wegen noch on <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verczieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> rihten und beczalen und sie darümb unklag
                        haft <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex><hi rend="sup">to</hi></expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>symon<ex>is</ex></expan> et jude.</ab>
</div>
